OL,5, The payments watchdog has proposed a   
OL,6, cap on fees that credit card firms such
OL,7, as Mastercard and Visa charge retailers
OL,8, for payments between the UK and the EU.
OL,10,FThe fees, which can get passed on to   
OL,11,Fconsumers, cost UK firms an extra #150m
OL,12,Fto #200m last year, the Payment Systems
OL,13,FRegulator (PSR) said.                  
OL,15,FThe payments giants have probably      
OL,16,Fraised fees to an "unduly high level"  
OL,17,Fsince Brexit, the regulator suggested. 
OL,19,FHowever, the firms disputed this, with 
OL,20,FVisa saying a cap was "not justified". 
